                "invention-title": [
                    "Geological carbon sequestration hydrogen production structure and method based on water-CO2-active mineral spontaneous reaction",
                    "基于水-CO2-活性矿物自发反应的地质固碳产氢结构及方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention discloses a geological carbon sequestration hydrogen production structure and method based on water-CO2-active mineral spontaneous reaction, and belongs to the technical field of carbon sequestration hydrogen production. The method comprises the following steps: (1) collecting carbon dioxide; (2) selecting a carbon sequestration hydrogen production place; (3) constructing a carbon sequestration hydrogen production space; (4) mineralizing and sealing carbon dioxide and synchronously producing hydrogen; and (5) hydrogen recovery. According to the method, the carbon dioxide is permanently mineralized and stored, and meanwhile, the water-CO2-active mineral reaction is utilized for synchronous geological hydrogen production, so that the economic cost of geological storage of the carbon dioxide is reduced, a new in-situ geological hydrogen production path can be developed, and green and low-carbon preparation of hydrogen energy is realized. The invention further provides a geological carbon sequestration hydrogen production structure, and the design and construction of the geological carbon sequestration hydrogen production structure have the functions of being low in sequestration cost and capable of achieving large-scale synchronous geological hydrogen production."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明公开了一种基于水‑CO2‑活性矿物自发反应的地质固碳产氢结构及方法，属于固碳制氢技术领域。本发明的方法包括如下步骤：(1)二氧化碳采集；(2)选择固碳产氢场所；(3)构建固碳产氢空间；(4)二氧化碳矿化封存及同步产氢；(5)氢气采收。该方法将二氧化碳永久矿化封存的同时，利用水‑CO2‑活性矿物反应进行同步地质制氢，不仅减少二氧化碳地质封存的经济成本，还能开辟原位地质制氢新路径，实现氢能绿色低碳制取。本发明还提供了一种地质固碳产氢结构，其设计构建具有封存成本低、可大规模同步地质制氢的功能。"
                }
            ]
        }
